The paper focuses on developing an agent with visual curiosity to learn visual recognition by asking questions to an Oracle. This involves reinforcement learning, visual recognition, question generation policy, answer digestion module, and graph memory module. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), and natural language processing (cs.CL) components, which are all relevant to the paper's content.
